      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c034e47337bcbbfd5f5529a"
      },
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Darius, just make sure that we don't get fooled by those Creed fanatics again, that ambush at Diik already cost us enough when Gray Noton appeared to try to capture Kamea.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 3,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c7d2279fbccbfa0de5a507c"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "59b98a97623035ac140056c6",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cd82b7adfcc35f3a8ca0c3e"
      },
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Don't worry, this time this is all cleared by the MRB so we should be safe from any contingencies and we are not facing the Legend-Killer again.\n\nAnd the TMM representative is also waiting for us to contact him on the planet's surface. ",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 4,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9cf151cc802ec42fc453c8bb"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "598cd3f26230355c18000069",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9ca0980c421068e1bf37364a"
      },
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Lady Elena Marisol-Chaplin?\n\nShe was the one who considered us persona non grata in the past years because of our association with Kamea, let's hope she doesn't find out about her still being on-board.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 5,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9cb4936d3c427028d5cb17dc"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "59b98a97623035ac140056c6",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
