    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9ccb26368d7ee5147c6d20bc"
      },
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Look everyone, despite us gaining access to the entire Hyades Rim, we are still quite restricted in our choice of employers, since the Taurians have been pushing forward with their colonization efforts, while pushing out any competitors to the natural resources of the area. ",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 6,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c906f271e3bd00e283b2ff8"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "59b98a97623035ac140056c6",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9ca1fdce5f119c26aec1bc97"
      },
      "index": 6,
      "text": "And while the Inner Sphere was clubbing itself back to the industrial age during the Third Succession War, the Concordat chose instead to focus in expansion efforts rather than waging war against its neighbors.\n\nHowever, with the Taurians being themselves, that also means a zero tolerance policy against unauthorized claims in what they now consider to be their territory.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 7,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c5115cd232058a389fb9b6d"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "59b98a97623035ac140056c6",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cda4d9ed45b2588ad76586b"
      },
      "index": 7,
      "text": "The Taurians can't control the entire rim, that's dozens of new worlds and colonies that have been reported in the region over the past decade.\n\nAnd a number of foreign megacorporations have also made investments in the area, and the taipans behind it will want some returns.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 8,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9cca0accddd4588bf0b58dce"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "598cd3f36230355c1800006a",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c2bcbe50a5a46fee9edcf56"
      },
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Which is exactly a great reason to attempt some reconciliation with Lady Marisol-Chaplin and the Taurian Defense Force, since we seem to be staying in the region for the medium term.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 9,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c5cfedb15d08a53ef2d45d8"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "59b98a97623035ac140056c6",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c1f94064bf2b2e853d567ee"
      },
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Mirfak is currently being colonized by three different groups, TMM and other megacorporations, the Far Lookers, and some independent efforts by Taurian citizens. \n\nOver the years, the Far Lookers have taken over most of the bureaucracy and lobbied hard, so the TDF has been forced to stay off world unless foreign interests threatened its security.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 10,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c3d78ddb5fec81a367ad8b3"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
