    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9ccac00cdea58d39dce8498c"
      },
      "index": 11,
      "text": "How well are you familiar with the Far Looker movement?",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 12,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c30620b077ff089ad9208d9"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c5ffb260b25b76dfd8d4fe1"
      },
      "index": 12,
      "text": "My father was a follower until he emigrated to Artru and married my mother but he distanced once they started raising a family.\n\nI still remember some of their literature in their housing unit about colonizing the Periphery.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 13,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9cbf0d4583ebb6ee7ec078cb"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c3c0b8bd810421de44bda2f"
      },
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Your parents were just like the typical Taurian citizen, who sympathizes with the movement.\n\nBut like every social tendency, the fanatics always follow along and with some of the Far Lookers have organized into a more militant faction calling themselves the Inheritors.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 14,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c485b6f6dcbe826f0b8a1ce"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c03da8c0947320882e24f8b"
      },
      "index": 14,
      "text": "We have heard about the Inheritors but our contact associated them with the Antithesis Creed, but it is not surprising what you are telling us, Lady Marisol-Chaplin, since there is a lot of overlap over their ideologies.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 15,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c6968f1bf90a2dfa91ff868"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9ccae776af4f8d874ccaf881"
      },
      "index": 15,
      "text": "And officially Protector Calderon supports the Far Looker ideology and has placed many of its supporters in government positions to speed up development of the Hyades Rim.\n\nBut the Concordat government disapproves of any radical ideology such as the Creed because of its controversial origins, this has caused a number of problems with the Inheritors and other groups in Mirfak.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 16,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9cfe06430d832d4174766d8a"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c0df0d6728dda36efffe261"
      },
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Since we can't risk any additional loss of life or property, the TDF has been requested by the TMM to deploy a 'Mech unit to contain the Inheritor radicals before the situation escalates.\n\nAnd the Taurian Constabulary has also gathered intelligence about a weapons build up.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "What are our orders?",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 17,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c991d061ca7a542253575b0"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c329bfefb087a274641fde2"
      },
      "index": 17,
      "text": "First, we need you to hit the supply convoys that the Inheritors are running to supply their base.\n\nOnce those are stopped, you will move in and take down their base, which should send a clear message to the rest of the Far Lookers.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "And what is the message Lady Marisol-Chaplin?",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 18,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c3428ffc5d9c18f7cda0549"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c6da099b77afec544c232b2"
      },
      "index": 18,
      "text": "This is Taurian territory, with Taurian rules.\n\nAnyone who disagrees or breaks them will be dealt with, and using the harsher terms possible.e",
